          <div class="content-block fade-in-up">
            <h2>1. Business Overview</h2>
            <p>Researchin Inc. is a technology startup that develops and operates "Researchin," an AI-driven matching platform that revolutionizes the participant recruitment process in academic research and corporate research and development (R&D). By seamlessly connecting researchers with high-quality research participants, we dramatically accelerate the research and development cycle and support innovation creation.</p>
            
            <h3>Mission and Vision</h3>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Mission:</strong> Provide a platform that accelerates research and eliminates innovation bottlenecks</li>
              <li><strong>Vision:</strong> Realize a society where anyone can easily participate in research and contribute to creating the future</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Business Opportunity</h3>
            <p>Traditional research participant recruitment requires significant time and cost, often resulting in only low-quality, biased samples. We have identified a massive business opportunity to dramatically improve research and development productivity by building a high-transparency two-sided marketplace using technology in this inefficient market.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section bg-light">
        <div class="container narrow">
          <div class="content-block fade-in-up">
            <h2>2. Market Analysis</h2>
            
            <h3>Market Size and Growth</h3>
            <p>R&D investment by domestic universities, research institutions, and private companies amounts to 3 trillion yen annually, with the participant recruitment-related market estimated at 20 billion yen. The wave of digital transformation (DX) is also reaching the research and development field, with rapid migration from traditional analog recruitment methods to efficient online platforms predicted.</p>

            <h3>Target Market</h3>
            <div class="service-detail">
              <h4>Researchers & Companies</h4>
              <p><strong>Persona:</strong> Researchers affiliated with universities, public research institutions, and corporate R&D departments</p>
              <p><strong>Needs:</strong> Quickly and cost-effectively gather high-quality participants and be freed from complex administrative work</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="service-detail">
              <h4>Research Participants</h4>
              <p><strong>Persona:</strong> General citizens, students, and people with specific conditions who are interested in social contribution and want to effectively utilize their free time</p>
              <p><strong>Needs:</strong> Safely participate in research in a trustworthy environment and receive fair compensation for their contribution</p>
            </div>

            <h3>Competitive Advantages</h3>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Technical Advantages:</strong> AI-powered recruitment optimization features provide unique value not found in competitors</li>
              <li><strong>Network Effects:</strong> The more researchers and participants gather on the platform, the better the matching quality and speed for both sides</li>
              <li><strong>Data Accumulation:</strong> Continuously improve matching algorithm accuracy by accumulating and analyzing recruitment and participation data</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
