            <h2>3. Platform Business Details</h2>
            
            <h3>"Researchin" Platform</h3>
            <p>A one-stop online platform connecting researchers and participants. Researchers can complete everything from recruitment page creation to participant management and reward payments online, while participants can easily search for and apply to research that matches their interests and conditions.</p>

            <h3>Problems and Solutions</h3>
            <div class="service-detail">
              <h4>Researcher Challenges and Solutions</h4>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Challenge:</strong> Participant recruitment takes months → <strong>Solution:</strong> Complete recruitment from thousands of participants in days</li>
                <li><strong>Challenge:</strong> Low-quality participants → <strong>Solution:</strong> Ensure quality through attribute filtering and evaluation systems</li>
                <li><strong>Challenge:</strong> Complex scheduling and payment processes → <strong>Solution:</strong> Automate administrative work to provide environment for research focus</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="service-detail">
              <h4>Participant Challenges and Solutions</h4>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Challenge:</strong> Few research participation opportunities → <strong>Solution:</strong> Provide access to diverse research projects</li>
                <li><strong>Challenge:</strong> Unclear safety → <strong>Solution:</strong> Ensure transparent information disclosure and thorough personal information protection</li>
                <li><strong>Challenge:</strong> Contributions not properly valued → <strong>Solution:</strong> Visualize contributions through clear reward systems</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

