            <p>Our revenue is centered on platform usage fees while diversifying through value-added services for researchers.</p>

            <h3>1. Platform Fees</h3>
            <div class="service-detail">
              <h4>Fee Model</h4>
              <p>We collect <strong>25%</strong> of the total reward amount for completed research participation as platform usage fees from researchers. Usage fees are invoiced monthly only, eliminating the traditional "individual procedures for each participant" and significantly reducing administrative burden.</p>
              
              <h4>(Future) Subscription Model</h4>
              <p>For companies and research institutions that frequently conduct large-scale recruitment, we will offer monthly/annual premium plans.</p>
            </div>

